window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Max is back! New husband, new job, and a training regime that cannot fail - to go wrong! </p> <p>Take one interim Chief Training Officer, add five recruits, mix with Joan of Arc, a baby mammoth, a duplicitous Father of History, a bombed rat, Stone Age hunters, a couple of passing policemen who should have better things to do, and Dick the Turd. Stir well, bring to the boil and wait for the bang! </p> <p>Join Max in the sixth instalment in the off-the-wall Chronicles of St Mary's series. </p>"; 
